METHODS OF DATA COLLECTION
****************************
1. Describe the methods for data collection and / or provide links to papers describing data collection methods
	Contains data obtained from meterological station across Nepal.
	Paper URL: https://climatenepal.org.np/resources/climate-change-trends-and-impacts-livelihood-people
	
