5. Analysis methods
	Trend Analysis for temperature and precipitations were done. 



************************
SUMMARY OF DATA FILES
************************
1. List of data files

	Filename: Summary of Precipitation Trends (mm per yr) in Nepal
	Short description: Summary of precipitation trends for time periods 1956-2006,1956-1976, 1977-2006

	Filename: Summary of Temperature Trends (°C per year) during 1975‐2006 in Nepal across Elevation Range
	Short description: Summary of temperature trends for elevation range 72-200m, 200-1000m, 1000-2000m, 
	greater than 2000m	

2. Relationships between files
	None 


